'''突破倡議'''<ref>{{cite news |author1=孙晨编 |title=霍金领衔富翁出钱 十年搜寻外星生命 |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/science/2015/07/150720_intelligent_life_search |accessdate=2020-10-29 |work=[[BBC|BBC中文]] |date=2015-07-20}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Breakthrough Initiatives}}）是一個由俄國科技業富豪[[尤里·米爾納|尤里·米爾納]]於2015年創建的計畫<ref>{{cite web |url=https://breakthroughinitiatives.org/about |title=Breakthrough Initiatives - About |accessdate= 2019-01-16}}</ref>。该计划準備在十年內投資1億美金尋找[[外星生命|外星生命]]。整個計畫分為幾個子項目。[[突破聆聽|突破聆聽]]項目將會尋找從超過100萬個恆星系統可能發射出來無線電或雷射信號。[[突破信息|突破信息]]項目準備設計出一條代表人類與地球的信息，在不久的將來送入太空<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.extremetech.com/extreme/210393-stephen-hawking-and-yuri-milner-unveil-100-million-initiative-to-dramatically-accelerate-search-for-alien-life|title=Stephen Hawking, Milner unveil $100M initiative to 'dramatically accelerate' search for alien life|last=Lendino |first=Jamie|date=20 July 2015|publisher=ExtremeTech |accessdate=20 July 2015}}</ref><ref name="NYT-20170628">{{cite news |last=Johnson |first=Steven |title=Greetings, E.T. (Please Don't Murder Us.) |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/28/magazine/greetings-et-please-dont-murder-us.html |date=28 June 2017 |work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]] |accessdate=28 June 2017 }}</ref>。[[突破攝星|突破攝星]]項目则与[[马克·扎克伯格|马克·扎克伯格]]合作，试图發射數千枚小探測器至最近星球半人馬座阿爾法星附近，速度高達[[光速|光速]]的20%。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://breakthroughinitiatives.org |title=Breakthrough Initiatives |work=Breakthrough Initiatives |date=2016-04-12 |accessdate=2016-04-12 }}</ref>突破观察项目准备识别和分类位于地球20光年以内的，类似地球的岩质行星<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://breakthroughinitiatives.org/Initiative/4|title=Breakthrough Initiatives|website=breakthroughinitiatives.org|language=en|access-date=2017-06-09}}</ref>。

